<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>以色列新闻RSS</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news</link><description></description><lastBuildDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 12:11:11 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>伊朗称已处决一名以色列摩萨德间谍</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-has-executed-an-israeli-mossad-spy/0000018c-7215-d798-adac-f6bfbe9f0000</link><description>伊朗官方媒体称，这名身份不明的男子与摩萨德等外国情报机构有联系，并被指控参与泄露机密信息</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 10:13:24 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/middle-east-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/iran-says-it-has-executed-an-israeli-mossad-spy/0000018c-7215-d798-adac-f6bfbe9f0000</guid></item><item><title>三名以色列人质被以色列国防军误杀后，数百人在特拉维夫集会</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-immediate-release-of-hostages/0000018c-71c6-db38-a9fc-f9e608ee0000</link><description>以色列士兵在加沙悲惨地杀害了三名人质，原因是他们被误认为是哈马斯成员，数百人走上特拉维夫街头，呼吁政府重返谈判桌并与哈马斯达成协议</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 09:33:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/hundreds-of-israelis-rally-in-tel-aviv-calling-for-immediate-release-of-hostages/0000018c-71c6-db38-a9fc-f9e608ee0000</guid></item><item><title>加沙武装分子在与以色列国防军的战斗中丧生；伊朗处决一名被指控为以色列摩萨德从事间谍活动的男子</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</link><description>两架敌对无人机从黎巴嫩渗透到以色列；一架被拦截，另一架坠毁 ■ 以色列国防军在加沙地带南部深化地面行动，在汗尤尼斯学校与哈马斯作战 ■ 伊朗处决了一名被指控为以色列摩萨德特工的男子 ■ 以色列国防军报告称，在加沙北部杀害了三名被误认为是威胁的以色列人质■ 航运巨头马士基因胡塞武装袭击而暂停红海航线 ■ 自 10 月 7 日以来，以色列至少有 1,200 名平民和士兵丧生；加沙至少有 130 名人质被扣押 ■ 哈马斯卫生部：加沙 18,608 人死亡，50,594 人受伤</description><pubDate>Sat, 16 Dec 2023 02:52:38 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-live/hundreds-protest-in-tel-aviv-after-three-hamas-hostages-mistakenly-killed-by-idf/0000018c-707c-d798-adac-f4ff14b20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列可以从纽约 9/11 清理和纪念活动中学到什么</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</link><description>以色列不应该清除南部 10 月 7 日灾难的废墟，而应该学习纽约在 9 月 11 日之后所做的事情</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 23:20:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-israel-can-learn-from-new-yorks-9-11-cleanup-and-commemoration/0000018c-6f95-db38-a9fc-efb71e8b0000</guid></item><item><title>如果定居者的暴力还不够，以色列现在正在剥夺约旦河谷巴勒斯坦人的水源</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</link><description>自战争爆发以来，约 20 个巴勒斯坦家庭因定居者暴力加剧而被迫离开约旦河谷的家园。与此同时，军队不让牧羊人社区获得水源。以色列志愿者日夜努力保护他们</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 22:24:03 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/twilight-zone/2023-12-16/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/if-settler-violence-wasnt-enough-israel-now-deprives-jordan-valley-palestinians-of-water/0000018c-6f70-dbd5-a39c-ff7344530000</guid></item><item><title>随着“后天”政府前景的临近，巴勒斯坦舞台在两极之间摇摆不定</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arena-swings-between-poles-as-prospect-of-day-after-government-looms/0000018c-6cef-d798-adac-ecefe2e80000</link><description>哈马斯领导人最近的声明并不是为以色列人准备的，哈马斯不是也不必成为与以色列就解决加沙问题进行谈判的伙伴。伊斯梅尔·哈尼亚和穆萨·阿布·马尔祖克的言论针对巴勒斯坦人</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 22:10:11 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-16/ty-article/.premium/palestinian-arena-swings-between-poles-as-prospect-of-day-after-government-looms/0000018c-6cef-d798-adac-ecefe2e80000</guid></item><item><title>以色列的“非殖民化”或巴勒斯坦人的“决定性失败”：这是我们唯一的选择吗？</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/decolonization-of-israel-or-total-defeat-of-palestinians-are-these-our-only-options/0000018c-6f0f-d692-a9dc-7f9f1b040000</link><description>暴行铭刻在两国人民的历史记忆中。领导人实时谈论“以色列的毁灭”和“2023 年加沙浩劫”。在把我们全部吐出来之前，这个地球能吸收多少血？</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:43:22 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.highlight/decolonization-of-israel-or-total-defeat-of-palestinians-are-these-our-only-options/0000018c-6f0f-d692-a9dc-7f9f1b040000</guid></item><item><title>就连左派也喜欢以色列的“好阿拉伯人”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/even-the-leftists-are-loving-israels-good-arabs/0000018c-6eb5-dbd5-a39c-fff7d7d20000</link><description></description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 21:22:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/opinion/2023-12-15/ty-article-opinion/.premium/even-the-leftists-are-loving-israels-good-arabs/0000018c-6eb5-dbd5-a39c-fff7d7d20000</guid></item><item><title>以色列抗议者因加沙人质问题与联合国秘书长对峙</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protesters-confront-un-chief-over-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-6ec2-d798-adac-eeeffd430000</link><description>人质被拖至加沙两个多月后，抗议者指责联合国秘书长安东尼奥·古特雷斯未能履行职责</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:28:40 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-protesters-confront-un-chief-over-hostages-held-in-gaza/0000018c-6ec2-d798-adac-eeeffd430000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队表示，他们在加沙北部杀害了三名人质，并被误认为是威胁</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-three-hostages-mistakenly-identified-as-threat-in-northern-gaza/0000018c-6edd-dbd5-a39c-ffff08470000</link><description>越狱并被以色列军队杀害的三名人质是 24 岁的 Samer Fuad El-Talalka、28 岁的 Yotam Haim 和 26 岁的 Alon Shamriz</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 20:15:54 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-says-killed-three-hostages-mistakenly-identified-as-threat-in-northern-gaza/0000018c-6edd-dbd5-a39c-ffff08470000</guid></item><item><title>“10 月 7 日发生的事情羞辱了以色列的男子气概。回应是暴力”</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-happened-on-october-7-humiliated-israeli-masculinity-the-response-is-violence/0000018c-68bb-de43-affd-fcbb5fe40000</link><description>美国心理学家、女权主义学者卡罗尔·吉利根 (Carol Gilligan) 帮助改变了人们对女性道德观念的思考。她对男女关系的见解也与加沙战争有关</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 19:58:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/what-happened-on-october-7-humiliated-israeli-masculinity-the-response-is-violence/0000018c-68bb-de43-affd-fcbb5fe40000</guid></item><item><title>为什么很少有巴勒斯坦电影讲述加沙的故事</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-so-few-palestinian-films-tell-the-story-of-gaza/0000018c-6eb4-db38-a9fc-efb65b370000</link><description>20 世纪 90 年代烧毁电影院的狂热分子；前往西岸寻找机会的电影制片人；哈马斯政权完全蔑视西方文化——所有这些都阻止了巴勒斯坦电影在大银幕上描绘加沙的生活。只有几部电影能够讲述一些故事</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 19:06:34 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.highlight/why-so-few-palestinian-films-tell-the-story-of-gaza/0000018c-6eb4-db38-a9fc-efb65b370000</guid></item><item><title>以色列内阁批准自战争开始以来首次通过凯雷姆沙洛姆过境点向加沙运送援助物资</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-approves-entry-of-aid-to-gaza-through-kerem-shalom-crossing/0000018c-6df6-db38-a9fc-edf610910000</link><description>美国安全顾问沙利文对这一在美国重压下获得批准的举措表示欢迎，并表示“我们希望这一新的开放将缓解拥堵，并有助于促进提供救生援助”</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 16:50:51 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-cabinet-approves-entry-of-aid-to-gaza-through-kerem-shalom-crossing/0000018c-6df6-db38-a9fc-edf610910000</guid></item><item><title>美国反犹太主义特使呼吁世界对哈马斯屠杀反应不一</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-antisemitism-envoy-calls-out-worlds-mixed-response-to-hamas-massacre/0000018c-6df8-db38-a9fc-edfa135a0000</link><description>黛博拉·利普斯塔特说，否认大屠杀花了几十年才产生影响。她告诉《国土报》，哈马斯同情者只需要四五天</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 16:34:56 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/.premium/u-s-antisemitism-envoy-calls-out-worlds-mixed-response-to-hamas-massacre/0000018c-6df8-db38-a9fc-edfa135a0000</guid></item><item><title>红海岸线：也门胡塞武装袭击的所有船只</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/red-sea-shipping-yemen-houthis-ships-attacked/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</link><description>在伊朗的支持下，也门胡塞武装使用巡航导弹、无人机和反舰弹道导弹瞄准以色列人拥有的船只或他们确定正在前往以色列的船只</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 16:17:58 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article-magazine/red-sea-shipping-yemen-houthis-ships-attacked/0000018c-5df7-d6f9-afbc-5dff7a430000</guid></item><item><title>胡塞武装加大对红海船只的攻击力度，但国际社会对此反应甚少</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-ships-in-red-sea-with-little-international-response/0000018c-6d6a-de43-affd-fd6ad2b60000</link><description>周四，两艘外国商船在红海和阿拉伯海遭到袭击。据报道，周五，胡塞武装继续向国际海上贸易施压，另一艘船在该地区遭到袭击</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:22:12 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/security-aviation/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/houthis-ramp-up-attacks-on-ships-in-red-sea-with-little-international-response/0000018c-6d6a-de43-affd-fd6ad2b60000</guid></item><item><title>以色列军队宣布三名士兵在加沙战斗中死亡</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-deaths-of-three-soldiers-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-6ddb-d798-adac-edff75360000</link><description>三名死去的以色列士兵是中士。 Shay Uriel Pizem 少校（预备），23 岁，中士。奥兹·什穆尔·阿拉迪 (Oz Shmuel Aradi)，19 岁，军士长。托梅尔·什洛莫·迈亚拉，28 岁</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:18:15 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-army-announces-deaths-of-three-soldiers-in-gaza-combat/0000018c-6ddb-d798-adac-edff75360000</guid></item><item><title>以色列边境警察在东耶路撒冷拍摄到袭击阿拉伯记者的画面</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officers-filmed-attacking-arab-journalist-in-east-jerusalem/0000018c-6da2-dbd5-a39c-fff36db10000</link><description>摄影记者穆斯塔法·哈鲁夫 (Mustafa Al-Haruf) 在东耶路撒冷瓦迪乔兹 (Wadi Joz) 社区记录周五的祈祷时遭到边防警察的袭击。两名涉事警员被停职，事件正在调查中</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 15:01:23 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/israeli-border-police-officers-filmed-attacking-arab-journalist-in-east-jerusalem/0000018c-6da2-dbd5-a39c-fff36db10000</guid></item><item><title>对美国武器的依赖迫使内塔尼亚胡接受拜登的战争要求</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/reliance-on-u-s-weapons-forces-netanyahu-to-accept-bidens-war-requests/0000018c-6d45-dbd5-a39c-ff7706f50000</link><description>这位美国总统正试图平衡他对以色列的支持和来自他的支持者的压力，以制定以色列的战时政策。事实证明，军事援助计划是美国对以色列的最佳筹码</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 13:29:33 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/.premium/reliance-on-u-s-weapons-forces-netanyahu-to-accept-bidens-war-requests/0000018c-6d45-dbd5-a39c-ff7706f50000</guid></item><item><title>“几乎完全有罪不罚的环境”：英国带头呼吁以色列解决定居者暴力问题 15 个国家</title><link>https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/britain-leads-15-nation-call-on-israel-to-tackle-west-bank-settler-violence/0000018c-6d31-d798-adac-edbf772b0000</link><description>法国、加拿大、澳大利亚等十几个国家强调，“以色列作为占领国，必须采取积极措施保护约旦河西岸的巴勒斯坦平民”。西方政府正在制定旅行禁令的标准，并正在收集相关名称</description><pubDate>Fri, 15 Dec 2023 11:57:07 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.haaretz.com/israel-news/2023-12-15/ty-article/britain-leads-15-nation-call-on-israel-to-tackle-west-bank-settler-violence/0000018c-6d31-d798-adac-edbf772b0000</guid></item></channel></rss>